1) Game tab(lower left window)->right-click->Add Tab->Profiler
    > lets you analyze game while it's running

2) Window(menu bar)->Layouts->Save Layout - save current Layout

3) popular format for models - FBX, textures - .PSD
    > Blender files (another file format for models) - contains source model data that can be edited inside Blender and take effect immediatly unlike FBX (need to download explicitely https://www.blender.org/download/)

4) assests can be combined in a bundle called Unity package (for example buy in Unity store)
    > Assests->Import Package->Custom Package->choose package in file system - import a package
    